\newlabel{fig:lr_schedule}{{10}{15}{Learning rate schedule. During the first 10 epochs, $\ell _r$ ramps up linearly from 0 to $10^{-3}$ (``warmup'') to avoid instability with random initial weights. Then it decays following a cosine curve to near 0 at epoch 200, allowing fine-grained convergence}{figure.caption.18}{}}
